long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Pin And Navigate To Your Best Answered Prompts on ChatGPT!

No More mindlessly scrolling and Time consuming perusing, go to your favourite answered prompt with ease. just click on the tack and navigate on click.

PromptTack was built to boost productivity, as a creator of multiple levels (a worker and student) I always get lost in my prompts when I'm in the zone and I don't like to waste my time perusing for the prompt that gave me the best answer that's why I create this extension for users of all ages and creators of all levels.


After installation , refresh the page and see the tacks/pins being appended, click on the pin and give your answered prompts a memorable title, click on the panel to go to your favourite prompt , rename at your will and remove them when you're done. that simple.
